edge: Horus is the son of Isis and Osiris
Horus is the son of Osiris, the king of Egypt
Isis is the wife of Osiris, the king of Egypt
Set is the brother of Osiris, the king of Egypt
Hathor is the lover of Horus, the Egyptian God of Air
Zaya is the lover of Bek, a young thief who allies with Horus
Ra is the father of Osiris and Set, the king of Egypt
Thoth is the brother of Horus, the Egyptian God of Air
Urshu is the second-in-command and architect of Set, the Egyptian God of the Desert
Isis and Nephthys are sisters and wives of Set
Astarte is one of the goddesses of war who are loyal to Set, the Egyptian God of the Desert
Anat is one of the goddesses of war who are loyal to Set, the Egyptian God of the Desert
Bek allies with Horus, the Egyptian God of Air
